records.name: Sorenzo Maldives

descriptions.hotel: Make yourself at home in one of the 15 guestrooms featuring minibars. Rooms have private balconies. Complimentary wireless internet access is available to keep you connected. Bathrooms have bathtubs or showers and hair dryers.
descriptions.direction: You'll be centrally located in Thoddoo with a stay at SORENZO Maldives , you'll be 9 minutes by foot from Thoddoo Beach. This beach guesthouse is within the region of Miyaru Faru Dive Site and Beyru Kandu Dive Site.
descriptions.general: In order to ensure the utmost level of relaxation, the guestrooms feature an inviting design and are equipped with all basic necessities, creating a delightful stay experience. To ensure your satisfaction, certain rooms in the bed & breakfast come fitted with air conditioning for a more pleasant stay.Within specific rooms, instant coffee and instant tea is conveniently available for your use.Understanding the significance of bathroom facilities in enhancing visitor contentment, bed & breakfast offers a hair dryer and toiletries within a few chosen chambers. Each day, arise to a delightful complimentary morning meal at Sorenzo Maldives.Throughout the day, engage in the entertaining activities available at Sorenzo Maldives.Unwind by the pool at bed & breakfast and cherish a leisurely moment.
descriptions.other: Featured amenities include a 24-hour front desk, luggage storage, and a water dispenser.
